{"lemma":"حَرِيقَة","slug":"حَرِيقَة","root":"ح.ر.ق","root_slug":"ح-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَرِيق","root":"حرق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7722"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"burnt"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fire, inferno, blaze","examples":[{"text":"أُصِيبَ سَبْعَةُ عُمَّالٍ عَلَى ٱلْأَقَلِّ فِي ٱلْحَرِيقِ","english":"At least seven workers were injured in the fire"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"nettle","tags":["collective"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħa.riːq/","/ħur.rajq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7722","headword_ar":"حَرِيقَةٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuroqapN","text_ar":"حُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also, (Yaakoob, S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaruwqapN","text_ar":"حَرُوقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of food,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thicker than what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasaA='","text_ar":"حَسَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Yaakoob, S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafiytap","text_ar":"نَفِيتَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which a little flour is sprinkled, and which swells,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becomes inflated, in boiling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and becomes of a whitish dust-colour: it is licked up with the tongue: and is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tfytp","text_ar":"تفيتة"},{"kind":"text","text":": they made use of it in hard and dear times, and when the cattle were lean, and when the season was severe: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was made by sprinkling flour upon water or fresh milk until it swelled, and became"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HsA'","text_ar":"حساء"},{"kind":"text","text":": a man used to satisfy his household with it when fortune overcame him: and it is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nfytp","text_ar":"نفيتة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (ISk, Az, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAy^iqu","text_ar":"حَرَايِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajadotu baniY","text_ar":"وَجَدْتُ بَنِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnK maA Eayo$N A_il~aA AlHaraAy^iqu","text_ar":"فُلَانٍ مَا عَيْشٌ اـِلَّا الحَرَايِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I found the sons of such a one having no means of subsistence other than the messes of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HrAy^q","text_ar":"حرايق"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA","ISk","Az"]}]}}